301
00:25:20,590 --> 00:25:22,590
Saet Byul, dan ayahmu makan prasmanan.

302
00:25:26,830 --> 00:25:28,059
Aku punya mobil.

303
00:25:29,959 --> 00:25:30,959
Mobil?

304
00:25:30,959 --> 00:25:32,999
Aku menyewa mobil atas nama kantor.

305
00:25:33,330 --> 00:25:34,600
Ada sopirnya juga.

306
00:25:36,569 --> 00:25:38,739
- Itu bagus.
- Aku mau pamer.

307
00:25:39,340 --> 00:25:42,309
"Kamu lihat? Kim Do Young sudah kembali."

308
00:25:43,479 --> 00:25:46,009
Orang-orang sangat peduli soal penampilan.

309
00:25:51,350 --> 00:25:52,450
Prasmanan?

310
00:25:54,219 --> 00:25:55,489
Tidak bisa.

311
00:25:58,160 --> 00:26:00,090
Menurutmu itu cukup?

312
00:26:00,259 --> 00:26:02,459
Lantas kita harus ke mana?

313
00:26:04,029 --> 00:26:06,100
Aku sudah menyesalinya.

314
00:26:06,999 --> 00:26:08,029
Menyesali apa?

315
00:26:08,170 --> 00:26:10,340
Berpisah denganmu.

316
00:26:11,539 --> 00:26:12,670
Kamu bisa menarik kata-katamu.

317
00:26:12,870 --> 00:26:14,340
Sungguh akan kulakukan.

318
00:26:15,370 --> 00:26:16,709
Aku akan sangat senang.

319
00:26:21,309 --> 00:26:22,450
Sebentar.

